data.description: Prime Location: 2417 Flagler Ave - The lowest-priced single-family home with a pool in Key West! The rotunda drive way allows for easy entry and exit to Flagler Avenue while accommodating multiple vehicles with ease. Impact doors, double-pane impact windows, and Bahama shutters result in low insurance rates. Inside, an open concept living and kitchen area features cathedral ceilings and wood plank porcelain tile. The updated kitchen features Quartz countertops, built in bar, pantry, wine fridge and stainless steel appliances. The 3 bedrooms have spacious closets and provide ample storage.  The pool features a heater, chiller, swim jet and jacuzzi and new equipment. Whether it's poolside gatherings, a soothing spa dip, or a workout with the resistance swim jet, this outdoor space is a dream. The fully fenced backyard offers both privacy and security and is complete with an outdoor shower. Walk straight into your laundry room from the poo areal for a seamless transition back into the comforts of home. The Azek decking front porch is perfect for sipping your morning coffee or enjoying a cool evening breeze. The 2 sheds on the property provide extra storage space for all your outdoor and recreational equipment.A Nest thermostat adds convenience and energy efficiency along with other Smart features in this home. Brand new 16-SEER energy efficient AC and air handler. Located in the middle of Key West, this property is close beautiful beaches, Garrison Bight Marina, Key West High School, shopping, and more! This is not a drive by, this is a property you must see in person.
